name: Mission Swasth Bharat
briefDescription: Mission Swasth Bharat is an India based non-profit organization registered by Government of India & Government of NCT of Delhi which is popularly known as “MSB” or “Mission”. It came into being as a seedling of the efforts of its President - Dr. B.R.J. Maharaj in the year 2007 as a Trust and thereafter as a Society in the year 2009 and started off with the idea of having a healthy, educated and developed India.To attain this objective, MSB started off by providing free treatments using techniques such as Acupressure, Ayurveda, Yunani, Homeopathic & Allopathic and thereafter gradually diversified into various other aspects, such as education & employment as well.
